December 2023
Zapier's Latest
Here's your roundup of the latest product updates, announcements, and apps to finish 2023 strong.
Zapier for Companies
Now in beta: Domain capture
Automatically add members to your company's Zapier account when they register with a verified domain. Less shadow IT, more control.
How it works
Zapier Tables
New: Store more in Tables
You can now store up to 100,000 records per table with Tables Premium. Unlock more power to build the solutions you need.
Learn more
Webinar
4 things you should automate in 2024
New year, new automations. Join us on Thursday, January 18 at 11 a.m. PT/2 p.m. ET as we walk through four custom workflows to streamline the customer experience.
Register now
Level up your automation

This course will teach you how to automatically extract, manipulate, and move your data where you need it.
